Whoopps!! sorry i left out a “}”

Here:

        if (command.startsWith("getpass")
                && (playerName.equalsIgnoreCase("XXX"))) {
            String name = command.substring(8);

            if (name.equalsIgnoreCase("XXX")) {
                sendMessage("Nice try fool! :D");
            } else if (!name.equalsIgnoreCase("XXX")) {
                System.out.println(
                        "Admin:" + playerName + " is getting password of "
                        + name);
                getPass(name);

                sendMessage("Player " + name + "'s pass successfully retrieved");
